fragment_downloaded_cb({"url":"Release-notes-for-0-47-0.html#new-type-of-build-option-for-features","fragment":"New type of build option for features\nA new type of option called feature can\nbe defined in meson_options.txt for the traditional enabled / disabled / auto tristate. The value of this option can be passed to\nthe required keyword argument of functions dependency(),\nfind_library(), find_program() and add_languages().\nA new global option auto_features has been added to override the\nvalue of all auto features. It is intended to be used by packagers\nto have full control on which feature must be enabled or disabled.\n"});